---

<ExplicitConstraints alt="explicit constraints">
- Do not explain or comment.
- Do no use and insert URL links.
- Do not stop mid-way. Convert the entire restaurant menu specified in <RestaurantMenu> block.
- Try to determine a single currency based on <RestaurantMenu> block.
- Set price for restaurant menu item only if price was provided.
- Keep all the items of the menu, but make it **as shorter as possible**.
</ExplicitConstraints>

---

<OutputFormat alt="rules regarding output format">
- The output must be an optimized content of <RestaurantMenu> block. Exclude all unnecessary information and <RestaurantMenu></RestaurantMenu> tags. Keep item names and prices.
- If the restaurant menu in <RestaurantMenu> block is not sufficient (e.g. empty), do not hallucinate, state that no menu information exist.
</OutputFormat>

